<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Enginia — Automatización con IA para Empresas en España</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Syne:wght@400;600;700;800&family=DM+Sans:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,500;1,300&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --ink: #0D0D0F;
    --paper: #F5F3EE;
    --accent: #FF4D1C;
    --accent2: #1A1AFF;
    --mid: #6B6B72;
    --border: rgba(13,13,15,0.1);
  }

  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  body {
    background: var(--paper);
    color: var(--ink);
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  /* NAV */
  nav {
    position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 100;
    padding: 18px 48px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
    background: var(--paper);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .logo {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 20px;
    letter-spacing: -0.5px;
  }
  .logo span { color: var(--accent); }
  .nav-cta {
    background: var(--ink);
    color: var(--paper);
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 14px;
    padding: 10px 22px;
    text-decoration: none;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    letter-spacing: 0.3px;
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }
  .nav-cta:hover { background: var(--accent); }

  /* HERO */
  .hero {
    min-height: 100vh;
    padding: 140px 48px 80px;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 48px;
    align-items: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -200px; right: -200px;
    width: 700px; height: 700px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,77,28,0.08) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .hero-label {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
    border: 1px solid var(--accent);
    padding: 5px 12px;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }

  h1 {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: clamp(40px, 5vw, 68px);
    line-height: 1.05;
    letter-spacing: -2px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  h1 em {
    font-style: normal;
    color: var(--accent);
    position: relative;
  }
  h1 em::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 4px; left: 0; right: 0;
    height: 3px;
    background: var(--accent);
    opacity: 0.3;
  }

  .subheadline {
    font-size: 19px;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--mid);
    max-width: 460px;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .cta-group { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; align-items: flex-start; }

  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--accent);
    color: #fff;
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 16px;
    padding: 16px 36px;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    text-decoration: none;
    display: inline-block;
    letter-spacing: 0.2px;
    transition: transform 0.15s, box-shadow 0.15s;
    box-shadow: 4px 4px 0 var(--ink);
  }
  .btn-primary:hover {
    transform: translate(-2px, -2px);
    box-shadow: 6px 6px 0 var(--ink);
  }
  .cta-microcopy {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--mid);
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  /* HERO VISUAL */
  .hero-visual {
    position: relative;
    height: 520px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  .process-diagram {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 440px;
    background: var(--ink);
    color: var(--paper);
    padding: 32px;
    position: relative;
  }
  .process-diagram::before {
    content: 'ANTES';
    position: absolute;
    top: -12px; left: 24px;
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    background: var(--accent);
    color: #fff;
    padding: 3px 8px;
  }
  .flow-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    padding: 10px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 300;
    opacity: 0.6;
  }
  .flow-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .flow-dot { width: 8px; height: 8px; background: #FF4D1C; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .flow-arrow { font-size: 18px; margin: 0 4px; opacity: 0.3; }

  .diagram-after {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0; right: -24px;
    width: 280px;
    background: var(--paper);
    border: 2px solid var(--ink);
    padding: 24px;
    box-shadow: 8px 8px 0 var(--accent);
  }
  .diagram-after::before {
    content: 'DESPUÉS';
    position: absolute;
    top: -12px; left: 16px;
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    background: var(--ink);
    color: var(--paper);
    padding: 3px 8px;
  }
  .metric-row {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: baseline;
    padding: 8px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .metric-row:last-child { border: none; }
  .metric-label { font-size: 12px; color: var(--mid); }
  .metric-val {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 22px;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  /* SOCIAL PROOF BAR */
  .proof-bar {
    background: var(--ink);
    color: var(--paper);
    padding: 32px 48px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 24px;
  }
  .proof-item {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 4px;
  }
  .proof-val {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 28px;
    color: var(--accent);
  }
  .proof-label {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: rgba(245,243,238,0.5);
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  }
  .proof-divider {
    width: 1px;
    height: 40px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
  }

  /* SECTIONS */
  section { padding: 100px 48px; }
  .section-label {
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  h2 {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: clamp(30px, 4vw, 48px);
    letter-spacing: -1.5px;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .section-intro {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--mid);
    max-width: 560px;
    margin-bottom: 60px;
  }

  /* PROBLEM */
  .problem-section { background: #F0EDE5; }
  .pain-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2px;
  }
  .pain-card {
    background: var(--paper);
    padding: 36px;
    position: relative;
  }
  .pain-number {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 64px;
    color: var(--border);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .pain-quote {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    font-style: italic;
  }
  .pain-consequence {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 500;
    padding-top: 16px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  /* SOLUTION */
  .solution-section {
    background: var(--ink);
    color: var(--paper);
  }
  .solution-section .section-label { color: var(--accent); }
  .solution-section h2 { color: var(--paper); }
  .solution-section .section-intro { color: rgba(245,243,238,0.5); }
  .solution-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 32px;
  }
  .solution-card {
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    padding: 36px;
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
  }
  .solution-card:hover { border-color: var(--accent); }
  .solution-icon {
    font-size: 32px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .solution-card h3 {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    letter-spacing: -0.5px;
  }
  .solution-card p {
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: rgba(245,243,238,0.65);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* HOW IT WORKS */
  .steps-section { background: var(--paper); }
  .steps-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2px;
    position: relative;
  }
  .step-card {
    background: #F0EDE5;
    padding: 48px 36px;
    position: relative;
  }
  .step-num {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 80px;
    color: rgba(13,13,15,0.06);
    line-height: 1;
    position: absolute;
    top: 24px; right: 24px;
  }
  .step-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .step-card h3 {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 22px;
    letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .step-card p {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--mid);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  .step-duration {
    margin-top: 24px;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--ink);
    padding: 6px 12px;
    background: var(--paper);
    display: inline-block;
  }

  /* PROOF */
  .proof-section { background: var(--paper); }
  .testimonials-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 32px;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }
  .testimonial {
    background: var(--ink);
    color: var(--paper);
    padding: 40px;
    position: relative;
  }
  .testimonial::before {
    content: '"';
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 120px;
    color: var(--accent);
    opacity: 0.3;
    position: absolute;
    top: -20px; left: 28px;
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .testimonial-text {
    font-size: 17px;
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }
  .testimonial-author {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 14px;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    padding-top: 20px;
  }
  .author-avatar {
    width: 42px; height: 42px;
    background: var(--accent);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 16px;
    color: #fff;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .author-name {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 15px;
  }
  .author-role {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: rgba(245,243,238,0.4);
  }

  .case-study-banner {
    background: var(--accent);
    color: #fff;
    padding: 48px;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
    gap: 24px;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .case-study-banner h3 {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 28px;
    letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .case-study-banner p {
    font-size: 16px;
    opacity: 0.85;
    font-weight: 300;
  }
  .case-big-num {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 72px;
    letter-spacing: -3px;
    line-height: 1;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .case-big-label {
    font-size: 13px;
    opacity: 0.8;
    text-align: center;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }

  /* OBJECTIONS */
  .objections-section {
    background: #F0EDE5;
  }
  .objections-grid {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2px;
  }
  .objection-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 2px;
  }
  .objection-q, .objection-a {
    padding: 32px 36px;
    background: var(--paper);
  }
  .objection-q {
    font-size: 17px;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--mid);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 16px;
  }
  .objection-q::before {
    content: '?';
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 32px;
    color: var(--border);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .objection-a {
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 500;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 16px;
  }
  .objection-a::before {
    content: '→';
    font-size: 20px;
    color: var(--accent);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  /* FINAL CTA */
  .final-cta {
    background: var(--ink);
    color: var(--paper);
    padding: 100px 48px;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .final-cta::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -200px; left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    width: 800px; height: 400px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,77,28,0.15) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .final-cta .section-label { color: var(--accent); }
  .final-cta h2 {
    color: var(--paper);
    max-width: 680px;
    margin: 0 auto 20px;
  }
  .final-cta .section-intro {
    margin: 0 auto 48px;
  }
  .urgency-note {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: rgba(245,243,238,0.4);
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    font-weight: 300;
  }
  .risk-reversal {
    margin-top: 24px;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: rgba(245,243,238,0.4);
    font-weight: 300;
  }
  .risk-reversal span { color: var(--paper); }

  /* FOOTER */
  footer {
    background: var(--ink);
    color: rgba(245,243,238,0.3);
    padding: 32px 48px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    font-size: 13px;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
  }
  footer .logo { color: var(--paper); font-size: 16px; }

  /* ANIMATIONS */
  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
    to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }
  .hero-content > * {
    animation: fadeUp 0.6s ease forwards;
    opacity: 0;
  }
  .hero-content > *:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0.1s; }
  .hero-content > *:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.25s; }
  .hero-content > *:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.4s; }
  .hero-content > *:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 0.55s; }
  .hero-visual {
    animation: fadeUp 0.8s 0.4s ease forwards;
    opacity: 0;
  }

  /* RESPONSIVE */
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    nav { padding: 16px 24px; }
    .hero { grid-template-columns: 1fr; padding: 120px 24px 60px; }
    .hero-visual { display: none; }
    section { padding: 72px 24px; }
    .proof-bar { padding: 28px 24px; }
    .pain-grid, .solution-grid, .steps-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .testimonials-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .objection-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .case-study-banner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; text-align: center; }
    footer { flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; text-align: center; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav>
  <div class="logo">engi<span>nia</span></div>
  <a href="#cta" class="nav-cta">Habla con nosotros →</a>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero" style="padding-top: 140px;">
  <div class="hero-content">
    <div class="hero-label">Enginia · Automatización con IA · España</div>
    <h1>Tu empresa trabaja.<br><em>Sin que nadie</em><br>lo haga manualmente.</h1>
    <p class="subheadline">Convertimos los procesos manuales de tu negocio en sistemas inteligentes que trabajan solos, para que tú puedas escalar sin contratar más.</p>
    <div class="cta-group">
      <a href="mailto:enginiagencia@gmail.com" class="btn-primary">Solicita tu auditoría gratuita →</a>
      <span class="cta-microcopy">En 30 minutos identificamos dónde estás perdiendo tiempo y dinero</span>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-visual">
    <div class="process-diagram">
      <div class="flow-row"><div class="flow-dot"></div> Recibir solicitud por email <span class="flow-arrow">→</span> copiar a CRM</div>
      <div class="flow-row"><div class="flow-dot"></div> Crear presupuesto en Word <span class="flow-arrow">→</span> enviar PDF</div>
      <div class="flow-row"><div class="flow-dot"></div> Hacer seguimiento manual <span class="flow-arrow">→</span> recordar llamar</div>
      <div class="flow-row"><div class="flow-dot"></div> Registrar en hoja Excel <span class="flow-arrow">→</span> actualizar stock</div>
      <div class="flow-row"><div class="flow-dot"></div> Emitir factura <span class="flow-arrow">→</span> enviar a contabilidad</div>
    </div>
    <div class="diagram-after">
      <div class="metric-row">
        <span class="metric-label">Horas ahorradas/semana</span>
        <span class="metric-val">22h</span>
      </div>
      <div class="metric-row">
        <span class="metric-label">Errores de proceso</span>
        <span class="metric-val">−91%</span>
      </div>
      <div class="metric-row">
        <span class="metric-label">Tiempo de respuesta</span>
        <span class="metric-val">4 min</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- SOCIAL PROOF BAR -->
<div class="proof-bar">
  <div class="proof-item">
    <span class="proof-val">+40</span>
    <span class="proof-label">Procesos automatizados</span>
  </div>
  <div class="proof-divider"></div>
  <div class="proof-item">
    <span class="proof-val">22h</span>
    <span class="proof-label">Ahorradas por empresa / semana</span>
  </div>
  <div class="proof-divider"></div>
  <div class="proof-item">
    <span class="proof-val">14 días</span>
    <span class="proof-label">Tiempo medio hasta primer resultado</span>
  </div>
  <div class="proof-divider"></div>
  <div class="proof-item">
    <span class="proof-val">100%</span>
    <span class="proof-label">Clientes sin equipo técnico previo</span>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- PROBLEM BLOCK -->
<section class="problem-section" id="problem">
  <div class="section-label">El problema</div>
  <h2>Reconoces esto.</h2>
  <p class="section-intro">No es falta de talento. Es que tu equipo pasa el día haciendo tareas que no requieren talento.</p>
  <div class="pain-grid">
    <div class="pain-card">
      <div class="pain-number">01</div>
      <p class="pain-quote">"Sé que hay herramientas de IA ahí fuera, pero cada vez que intento implementar algo acabo tres días después sin nada funcionando y sintiéndome idiota."</p>
      <p class="pain-consequence">Resultado: sigues pagando a personas para hacer trabajo de máquina, y cada mes que pasa tu competencia se distancia más.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="pain-card">
      <div class="pain-number">02</div>
      <p class="pain-quote">"No puedo escalar porque necesitaría contratar a tres personas más. Y no tengo ni presupuesto ni tiempo para formarlas."</p>
      <p class="pain-consequence">Resultado: rechazas proyectos buenos o los aceptas y entregas tarde. Tu reputación paga el precio del crecimiento.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="pain-card">
      <div class="pain-number">03</div>
      <p class="pain-quote">"Mis procesos están todos en la cabeza de una persona. Si esa persona se va mañana, tenemos un problema serio."</p>
      <p class="pain-consequence">Resultado: tu empresa depende de individuos, no de sistemas. Eso no es un negocio, es un trabajo con logo.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- SOLUTION BLOCK -->
<section class="solution-section" id="solution">
  <div class="section-label">La solución</div>
  <h2>Lo que cambia cuando<br>trabajas con Enginia.</h2>
  <p class="section-intro">No te vendemos software. Te construimos el sistema operativo que tu empresa necesitaba desde hace dos años.</p>
  <div class="solution-grid">
    <div class="solution-card">
      <div class="solution-icon">⚡</div>
      <h3>Tus operaciones corren solas</h3>
      <p>Cada lead que entra, cada pedido, cada solicitud de cliente se procesa, clasifica y responde automáticamente. Tu equipo se entera del resultado, no del proceso.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="solution-card">
